n    :target: https://github.com/renatonlima\n    ```\n---\n\n# Brazilian Localization WMS Accounting\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:3efbdeddb3856fe79082ccce3fc517e82235e5a4313f5e8282e617a00431ce0a\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module make possible create invoice based in Stock Pickings.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Installation\n\nThis module depends on:\n\n- stock_account\n- stock_picking_invoicing\n- l10n_br_stock\n- l10n_br_account\n\n## Configuration\n\nNo configuration required.\n\n## Usage\n\nGo to Picking and in Additional Information select the field 'Invoice\nState', if choosed 'To be Invoice' should be inform the Fiscal Operation\nand the Taxes after Confirm and Tranfer the Picking an button will\nappear to 'Create Invoice' with the possibility to create invoice based\nin Grouped Pickings.\n\n## Known issues / Roadmap\n\n## Changelog\n\n### 14.0.3.2.1 (2023-09-07)\n\n**Bugfixes**\n\n> - Fixes picking creation with kits products.\n\n### 13.0.1.0.0 (2022-01-19)\n\n- Module migration.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_br_stock_account%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Akretion\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Akretion](https://akretion.com/pt-BR):\n\n  - Renato Lima \\<<mailto:renato.lima@akretion.com.br>>\n\n- [Kmee](https://www.kmee.com.br):\n\n  - Gabriel Cardoso de Faria \\<<mailto:gabriel.cardoso@kmee.com.br>>\n\n### Other credits\n\nThe development of this module has been financially supported by:\n\nAKRETION LTDA - [www.akretion.com](http://www.akretion.com)\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainers](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-renatonlima }} {{ maintainer-mbcosta }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-brazil](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-brazil/tree/16.0/l10n_br_stock_account) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_stock_account.models.stock_picking_type", "documentation": ["Copyright (C) 2011  Renato Lima - Akretion", "License AGPL-3 - See http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_stock_account.models.stock_picking_type.StockPickingType", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_stock_account.models.stock_picking_type.StockPickingType._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_stock_account.models.stock_picking_type.StockPickingType.fiscal_operation_id", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.l10n_br_stock_account.models.stock_picking_type.StockPickingType.pre_generate_fiscal_document_number", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_cla